[6] Canada & USA update
Date: Tue 31 Mar 2015
Source: Outbreak News Today [edited]
http://outbreaknewstoday.com/measles-update-for-the-us-and-canada-89761/


For the 1st time in 2 weeks, the California Department of Public Health reported a new confirmed measles case in a Los Angeles [California, USA] resident. This brings the total cases in California to 134 since December 2014.

Nationally, the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) puts the measles tally at 178 people from 17 states and the District of Columbia up to 27 Mar 2015.

The measles outbreak in Quebec, Canada has grown by 8 cases as the total as of today stands at 158.

[Byline: Robert Herriman]

